WallBlend! is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application.

Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:

Personal Information:
When you sign up for WallBlend! through email we collect personal information, such as:

Name
Email Address
User ID (from Firebase Authentication)
Uploaded Content:
When you upload wallpapers or other content through the app, we collect:

Images and other media that you upload
Categories associated with your uploaded wallpapers
Timestamp of when the content was uploaded
Device Information:
We may collect non-personal information related to your device, including:

Device model
Operating system version
Unique device identifiers
Usage Information:
We collect information on how you interact with the App, such as:

Pages viewed
Buttons clicked
Time spent on different sections of the App
How We Use the Information
The information we collect is used to:

Provide, maintain, and improve the services and features of the App.
Personalize your experience and show wallpapers based on your preferences.
Allow you to upload, categorize, and share wallpapers.
Communicate with you regarding updates, features, and customer support.
We do not share, sell, or rent your personal information to third parties.

Firebase Services
We use Firebase services, including:

Firebase Authentication: For secure login and user account management.
Firebase Firestore: To store user-uploaded wallpapers and their associated categories.
Firebase Storage: To store images and media files uploaded by users.
Google's privacy policy can be viewed here.

Data Security
We are committed to safeguarding the security of your data. We use industry-standard encryption and security protocols to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Data Retention
We retain your personal information and uploaded content for as long as your account is active or as necessary to provide services to you. If you wish to delete your account or request that we delete your uploaded content, please contact us at the email provided below.

Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access the personal information we hold about you.
Request the correction or deletion of your personal information.
Object to the processing of your personal information.
Withdraw your consent to the collection and use of your data at any time.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or change this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review this policy periodically for updates.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: gkyando5@gmail.com
by developer: goodluck abisai kyando

Chinese Version

当然可以！以下是您的隐私政策的中文翻译：

WallBlend! 隐私政策

WallBlend! 致力于保护您的隐私。本隐私政策概述了我们在您使用我们的移动应用程序时如何收集、使用和保护您的个人信息。

我们收集的信息

我们收集以下类型的信息：

个人信息：

当您通过电子邮件注册 WallBlend! 时，我们会收集个人信息，例如：

姓名

电子邮件地址

用户 ID (来自 Firebase 身份验证)

上传的内容：

当您通过应用程序上传壁纸或其他内容时，我们会收集：

您上传的图像和其他媒体

与您的上传壁纸相关的类别

内容上传的时间戳

设备信息：

我们可能会收集与您的设备相关的非个人信息，包括：

设备型号

操作系统版本

唯一设备标识符

使用信息：

我们收集您如何与应用程序互动的信息，例如：

查看过的页面

点击的按钮

在应用程序不同部分花费的时间

我们如何使用这些信息

我们收集的信息用于：

提供、维护和改进应用程序的服务和功能。

个性化您的体验并根据您的偏好展示壁纸。

允许您上传、分类和分享壁纸。

与您沟通有关更新、功能和客户支持的信息。

我们不会将您的个人信息共享、出售或出租给第三方。

Firebase 服务

我们使用 Firebase 服务，包括：

Firebase 身份验证：用于安全登录和用户帐户管理。

Firebase Firestore：存储用户上传的壁纸及其相关类别。

Firebase 存储：存储用户上传的图像和媒体文件。

Google 的隐私政策可以在此查看。

数据安全

我们致力于保护您的数据安全。我们使用行业标准的加密和安全协议来保护您的个人信息。然而，互联网传输或电子存储的方法没有任何一种是 100% 安全的，我们不能保证绝对的安全性。

数据保留

我们会在您的账户活动期间或在必要提供服务的情况下保留您的个人信息和上传内容。如果您希望删除账户或请求我们删除您上传的内容，请通过以下提供的电子邮件联系我们。

您的权利

您有权：

访问我们持有的关于您的个人信息。

请求更正或删除您的个人信息。

反对处理您的个人信息。

随时撤回您对数据收集和使用的同意。

本隐私政策的更改

我们保留随时更新或更改本隐私政策的权利。任何更改将发布在此页面上，我们鼓励您定期查看此政策以获取更新信息。

联系我们

如果您对本隐私政策有任何疑问或担忧，请联系我们：

电子邮件：gkyando5@gmail.com

开发者：Goodluck Abisai Kyando

希望这对您有帮助！如果有其他问题，请告诉我。
